{
  "stem": "20581.4",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they said to me that they know that I'm-- I have to stay with them.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I'm not going to the camp.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I have to work.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I have to join the Berihah.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They heard about me, that I am capable to do these things, I have to stay.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I said, OK.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I was not married in that time.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I had nothing to lose.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Berihah means flight in Hebrew.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, it actually was what we called it-- flight and rescue.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "This was an organization which-- it started out like, we the-- were the one who started out the illegal immigration [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So when I came to Vienna after being there a few weeks, getting to know some people, so, we had to do some work.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So, they gave me a mission.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They told me I had to go to Lithuania to pick up a young kibbutz, people from a kibbutz to work, 26 people that time.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Of course, the guy who was running the Berihah-- his name was [?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yitzak ?] [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "His wife was also one of them.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So actually, what he wanted me to do, I should go ahead and bring back his wife plus these people.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] To tell you the story what have happened, I'm gonna give you some information.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] They made-- we-- they gave me papers that I work for the International Red Cross.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And I also had a-- I was going-- a friend of my-- I met a friend of mine.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I mean, I got to know him.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He was a Vienna-born Jew.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So he gave me his passport.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We falsified a passport that my name was [?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Wilhelm ?] [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And in that time, the transportation was very hard.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
